niences you could hope for and more but at night there were male street walkers so you may want to be wary of taking your kids out at night.OVERALL: I would say the hotel was a great place to stay for the price, especially considering some of the other ones I've seen, but it would be my last choice for what I would consider to be a 3-4 star hotel. Double check where your room would be located and make sure there not renovating next to it and park across the street instead of using the parking spots that they &quot;provide&quot;.	
